CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 8, 1962, pg. 18 reads: "Making Presentation - Mrs. Marion E.Bryant (third from left), first vice president of the National Association of Business and Professional Women, Inc., presents a gift from the Pittsburgh club of the NBPA to Mrs. Florence Ball Jones (third from right) at the 40th anniversary celebration of the local group last Sunday. Mrs. Jones is a charter member of the Pittsburgh club.  Left to right: Mmes Betty Moore, Mary Burwell, Daisy E. Lampkin, Lenore Rainey, president; Cora B. Jones and Alma A. Polk. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of sixteen women, including Florence Ball Jones, seated center, gathered in Bethesda Presbyterian Church for the National Association of Business nad Professional Women, Inc. fortieth anniversary celebration
